Title: An Act Changing the Name of the Sta. Lucia Elementary School in Barangay Kabayanan, Municipality of San Juan, Metropolitan Manila, to Mababang Paaralan Ng Kabayanan
Data:
BATAS PAMBANSA BLG. 662
An Act Changing the Name of the Sta. Lucia Elementary School in Barangay Kabayanan, Municipality of San Juan, Metropolitan Manila, to Mababang Paaralan Ng Kabayanan
Section 1. The name of the Sta. Lucia Elementary School in Barangay Kabayanan, Municipality of San Juan, Metropolitan Manila, is hereby changed to Mababang Paaralan ng Kabayanan.1Ã¢wphi1
Section 2. This Act shall take effect upon its approval.
Approved: March 7, 1984
